Name: oid
column6: row identifier (hidden attribute; must be explicitly selected)

Name: defaclrole
column6: the oid of the role associated with this entry

Name: defaclnamespace
column6: the oid of the namespace associated with this entry, or 0 if none

Name: defaclobjtype
column6: type of object this entry is for: r = relation (table, view), s = sequence, f = function, t = type, n = schema

Name: defaclacl
column6: access privileges that this type of object should have on creation
